    public class ProductOneSEVPA<L1,L2,I>
extends AbstractOneSEVPA<Pair<L1,L2>,I>
    Production automaton that allows to join two given 1-SEVPAs. Acceptance semantics of the product automaton depends on the given AcceptanceCombiner.
    Author:
    Malte Isberner
